<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ban-vt">ban <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bæn/    美 /bæn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-prohibit">1.★ <strong>禁止；取缔(prohibit)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Government has banned the use of chemical weapons. 
政府已经禁止使用化学武器。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>ban sb from (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was banned from athletics for two years after failing a drug test.
她没通过药检，被禁赛两年。</p></div></div>